---
import FooterLink from './footer-link.astro';
import FooterSocial from './footer-social.astro';

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer>
  <div class="mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pb-12 lg:pb-16 max-w-7xl">
    <div class="border-gray-200 bg-white border-t w-full"></div>

    <div class="xl:gap-12 xl:grid xl:grid-cols-3 mt-6 pt-6">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
          <span class="block mb-4">
            👋 What? Still here? Scrolling all the way down?
            <em>Impressive dedication</em> to... absolutely nothing.
          </span>

          <span class="block mb-4">
            Look at you go! Reading footer text like it's gonna reveal
            some ancient wisdom or something. Spoiler alert: it won't.
            Here's your reward: 🎉 (it's just an emoji, deal with it)
          </span>

          <span class="block">
            Maybe go touch some grass? Or count ceiling tiles?
            Both equally productive as reading this.
            Bye! 👋
          </span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="gap-12 grid col-span-2 mt-12 xl:mt-0">
        <div class="md:gap-12 md:grid md:grid-cols-[auto_1fr]">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm leading-6">Projects</h3>
            <ul role="list" class="space-y-3 mt-6">
              <li><FooterLink href="https://github.com/Mati365/ts-c-compiler">C Compiler in JS</FooterLink></li>
              <li><FooterLink href="https://github.com/Mati365/ckeditor5-rails">CKEditor 5 Ruby on Rails integration</FooterLink></li>
              <li><FooterLink href="https://github.com/Mati365/upolujksiazke.pl">UpolujKsiazke.pl</FooterLink></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-10 md:mt-0">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm leading-6">Resources</h3>
            <ul role="list" class="space-y-3 mt-6">
              <li><FooterLink href="#">🐹 My technical interview with a guinea pig about CORS</FooterLink></li>
              <li><FooterLink href="https://shattereddisk.github.io/rickroll/rickroll.mp4"></FooterLink></li>
              <li><FooterLink href="https://www.wikihow.com/Make-Salt-Water">Salt Water Recipe</FooterLink></li>
              <li><FooterLink href="mailto:cziken58@gmail.com">Contact</FooterLink></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

